data.description: Welcome to you Dream House, locate in a gated Guard community 24/7 of Woodland Lakes Preserve. this beautiful home 5 bedrooms 3 bathroom and large office that can be the 6th room, has also a very convenient guest room in first floor with full bathroom. open kitchen with full upgrade stainless steel appliances, digital stove oven with air fryer, breakfast area, granite countertop, hardwood floor on first floor, stair and 2nd floor. Large Master room with large bathroom with separate tub and walk in-shower upstairs also laundry room and office room. The roof was replaced 2018 and new gutter was installed in 2023, the A/C in 2020. Full fenced backyard with conservation area on back. The property is near Waterford Lake Town center, easy access with 408 and417 highways, Lake Nona Medical City, Orlando International Airport and UCF
